having a lesson with...

16:07.067 --> 16:08.267
- Yeah.
- The best.

16:08.268 --> 16:09.335
- He is.
- He's the best.

16:09.336 --> 16:11.037
- I know.
- Very lucky.

16:11.038 --> 16:13.072
Thank you.
We're trying to...

16:13.073 --> 16:14.540
- Can I talk to you?
- Can you... Yeah.

16:14.541 --> 16:16.875
