just a minute, Maestro.

16:16.876 --> 16:18.044
- Come with me.
- Okay.

16:18.045 --> 16:20.313
- Hai Lai.
- Yes, what?

16:21.381 --> 16:23.649
Do you want to have
a child with me?

16:23.650 --> 16:24.816
What?

16:24.817 --> 16:27.053
Let's have a child, you and me.

16:27.054 --> 16:29.121
Uh, I'll be right there.

16:29.122 --> 16:30.922
