16:47.507 --> 16:48.740
Hey.

16:48.741 --> 16:50.076
Cynthia.

16:50.077 --> 16:51.843
- Maestro.
- Hey.

16:51.844 --> 16:54.080
Wow. This is really good.

16:54.081 --> 16:55.381
Ah, yeah, it works for me.

16:55.382 --> 16:57.083
Yes, yes, I'll do this for you.

16:57.084 --> 16:58.550
I can move in. Yeah, yeah.

16:58.551 --> 17:00.119
- What?
- Stay here. Yeah.

17:00.120 --> 17:02.288
You know, I stayed
with Gloria last time.

17:02.289 --> 17:04.089
I can stay here. Why not?

17:04.090 --> 17:05.457
It'll be fun.

17:05.458 --> 17:06.625
So wait.

17:06.626 --> 17:08.227
Bradford's not coming
to the opening?

17:08.228 --> 17:10.429
No. He's touring
with his documentary.

17:10.430 --> 17:12.763
- Hmm.
- It's really important
to him, you know?

17:12.765 --> 17:15.467
Yeah, and this really
matters to you.
He should be here.

17:15.468 --> 17:17.769
Yeah, he should really
be here, shouldn't he?

17:17.770 --> 17:19.738
Yes.

17:19.739 --> 17:20.739
What about Rodrigo?

17:20.740 --> 17:22.108
Is he gonna make it
for your big moment?

17:22.108 --> 17:23.474
Yeah, I was going to invite him,

17:23.476 --> 17:25.777
and then he, like, asked me
to have a child with him.

17:25.778 --> 17:26.912
Wait. What?

17:26.913 --> 17:28.714
Yeah, he was not being serious.

17:28.715 --> 17:29.981
How do you know?

17:29.982 --> 17:31.551
Because I know him.

17:32.752 --> 17:33.952
Have you ever just, like,

17:33.953 --> 17:37.289
asked Rodrigo what
the deal is with you two?

17:37.290 --> 17:39.658
No. I don't need to.
I know what the deal is.

17:39.659 --> 17:40.693
There isn't one.

17:41.861 --> 17:43.195
Okay.

17:43.196 --> 17:44.563
Just as long as you're not,

17:44.564 --> 17:46.333
you know, waiting
around for him.

17:54.574 --> 17:55.542
Ai, 'mano.

17:55.543 --> 17:57.143
'mano.

17:57.144 --> 17:59.044
It's the fucking five flights up

17:59.045 --> 18:01.347
and the five flights down.

18:09.922 --> 18:12.824
Uh, ¿quiéres algo a beber?

18:12.825 --> 18:14.160
Uh...

18:14.161 --> 18:15.227
una cerveza, por favor.

18:15.228 --> 18:16.295
Dos, dos, dos.

18:16.296 --> 18:17.396
Y un tequila.

18:17.397 --> 18:19.698
Yo no, yo no.
No yo.

18:19.699 --> 18:21.167
Ah, sí.

18:21.168 --> 18:22.034
Cynthia. Look, look,

18:22.035 --> 18:23.068
Cynthia.

18:23.069 --> 18:25.003
Huh? My toca box.

18:25.004 --> 18:26.605
- What is that?
- Heh heh.

18:32.412 --> 18:33.912
Estoy bien.

18:33.913 --> 18:36.382
You know, Maestro Rivera,
he took it away from me.

18:36.383 --> 18:38.417
He took it away from me,
and he locked it up.

18:38.418 --> 18:40.186
He locked it up
with all my things.

18:40.187 --> 18:41.321
He locked it.

18:52.732 --> 18:55.734
- Mira.
- Ha ha!

19:10.783 --> 19:11.917
Hey, hey, no, no, no.

19:11.918 --> 19:13.220
No, no. Hey, Rodrigo.

19:27.234 --> 19:28.701
Mira.

19:38.811 --> 19:40.813
Claro Que sí, Maestro.

19:54.894 --> 19:56.495
Look at this crowd.

19:56.496 --> 19:57.896
Half of Wall Street is here.

19:57.897 --> 20:00.065
I'm half expecting the SCC
to kick the door down.

20:00.066 --> 20:03.134
Yes. I'm going to make
my money back tonight.

20:03.135 --> 20:04.703
I can feel it. I don't care

20:04.704 --> 20:08.106
if I have to rifle through
pockets in the coat room.

20:08.107 --> 20:09.441
Sorry. What was that?

20:09.442 --> 20:10.942
We're doing great financially.

20:10.943 --> 20:13.245
That was a joke and
totally off the record.

20:13.246 --> 20:14.747
If you wouldn't mind stepping...

20:16.249 --> 20:17.583
Oh, my goodness.

20:17.584 --> 20:20.118
You look magnificent.

20:20.119 --> 20:21.687
Excuse me.
I have to work.

20:21.688 --> 20:23.222
- Oh, well...
- Ouch.

20:29.862 --> 20:30.962
Hey.

20:30.963 --> 20:32.464
Hey.

20:32.465 --> 20:35.200
So, uh, before?

20:35.201 --> 20:36.335
Hmm? Oh.

20:36.336 --> 20:39.137
Yeah, that was a bit much.

20:39.138 --> 20:40.407
Uh-huh.

20:42.174 --> 20:43.775
You know dark matter?

20:43.776 --> 20:44.577
What?

20:44.578 --> 20:46.244
Dark matter, you know?

20:46.245 --> 20:49.080
Yeah, the thing
that's all around us.

20:49.081 --> 20:51.950
Do you know why we know
it's around us?

20:51.951 --> 20:53.352
No.

20:53.353 --> 20:56.087
Because the universe
is expanding

20:56.088 --> 20:58.189
and contracting
at the same time.

20:58.190 --> 21:02.127
See? Changing it out
and changing it in.

21:02.128 --> 21:03.762
- Right.
- Like the present.

21:03.763 --> 21:04.731
Hmm.

21:04.732 --> 21:07.367
Are you ready for
the changes, Hailey?

21:08.868 --> 21:09.868
Yeah.

21:09.869 --> 21:11.937
I think they're
already happening.

21:21.814 --> 21:23.949
I guess I'm
in the doghouse again.

21:23.950 --> 21:25.150
So what did you do?

21:25.151 --> 21:26.585
I don't know what I did.

21:26.586 --> 21:28.487
I drove her to Long Island
and drove her back.

21:28.488 --> 21:29.521
I don't know.

21:29.522 --> 21:31.690
Maestro. Hi. Hello.

21:31.691 --> 21:34.159
Um, I will just cut
right to the chase.

21:34.160 --> 21:37.729
