21:42.769 --> 21:44.870
- That's fantastic.
- It is fantastic,

21:44.871 --> 21:46.572
and it's exciting,
and it's dark,

21:46.573 --> 21:48.574
and it's brave,
and it's very sad,

21:48.575 --> 21:50.576
and... and the space
that I want to conduct it at

21:50.577 --> 21:52.611
