art space in Brooklyn.

21:52.612 --> 21:54.780
- It's very cool.
- Oh, you should do it.

21:54.781 --> 21:55.748
Are you mad?

21:55.749 --> 21:58.717
You are a minor
electronic music star.

21:58.718 --> 21:59.619
