22:10.797 --> 22:13.532
All right, that's
enough. Go on. Uh...

22:13.533 --> 22:15.401
Come on, come on.

22:15.402 --> 22:16.903
- All right.
- Yes.

22:18.037 --> 22:19.438
There'll be conditions.

22:54.340 --> 22:55.874
Bravo!

22:55.875 --> 22:57.877
Bravo, bravo!

23:00.547 --> 23:02.180
Thank you all.
Thank you all.

23:02.181 --> 23:03.749
Thank you so much for coming.

23:03.750 --> 23:06.317
