23:12.725 --> 23:14.125
She has such a big heart.

23:14.126 --> 23:16.027
She has such a big heart,

23:16.028 --> 23:17.629
Gloria Windsor, right?

23:17.630 --> 23:19.798
Yeah, a big heart, like a horse.

23:20.833 --> 23:21.634
Like a horse?

23:21.635 --> 23:23.068
Uh, thank you, Maestro.

23:23.069 --> 23:24.003
Thank you.

23:24.004 --> 23:26.905
Everyone here has
a big horse heart

23:26.906 --> 23:29.675
because we care about this city,

23:29.676 --> 23:32.343
this orchestra, and that's
why we're so excited

23:32.344 --> 23:35.180
