Darling, we had no idea.

25:03.002 --> 25:04.836
Uh, yes, we're
full of surprises.

25:04.837 --> 25:07.840
- Yes.
- We are full of them.

25:09.341 --> 25:10.642
Oh, can we have this room

25:10.643 --> 25:12.210
